<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bangkimbawlthei - Pa Pathien,
 Lei leh van - Siempa chuh ka ging.

[V2]
 2. A Cha neihsun I-su Krista,
 Amah le ka ging hi.

[V3]
 3. Amah chuh Thagau Thiengtho in A-vawpsak a,
 A nungak laiin Mari'n cha'n a nei.

[V4]
 4. Pontia Pilat in nasa takin a-gim bawl a,
 Khetden in a uma.

[V5]
 5. A thi ta a,
 Vuih n a um ta a.

[V6]
 6. Mithi khuo chu A-zu tawh a,
 Ni thum ni chun mithi lak apat-in A tho ta a.

[V7]
 7. Van ah A kal-to kit a,
 Bangkimbawlthei Pa Pathien changlam ah-A va chu ta a.

[V8]
 8. Zie apat chun hung kum-kit ina,
 Mhing leh mithi-vaihawm sak ding in.

[V9]
 9. Chun, Thagau Thiengtho-ka gingchai,
 Mi chengcheng di'n Sapchuom thiengtho-um hi ka gingchai.

[V10]
 10. Mi thiengtho haw kivawp khawm hi-ka gingchai,
 Mawh ngaihdamna ka ging.

[V11]
 11. Sapum thawkitna le ka ging.
 Kumkhuo a hinna tawh, Amen.</lyrics>
<title>GLORIA PATRI. NO. 1</title>
</song>